/div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jmsp867\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51b6bfbf7492113d4e8664eb17571a34?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/51b6bfbf7492113d4e8664eb17571a34?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jmsp867\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jmsp867</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great job. Thanks</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great Evolution</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gardenmgt\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b20311e2e3cb2a77e3290c68982b7a6e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/b20311e2e3cb2a77e3290c68982b7a6e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/gardenmgt\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Gardenmgt</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">As other forms of Internet Platforms have evolved Wordpress has been able to surpass what was expected of a leader in websites and optional plugins.  The block system isn\'t new, but blocks certainly make building and maintaining websites easier.  The plugin systemization allows me to taylor the websites to specific needs without bulking up the backend code, slowing down delivery and being dinged by search engines.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:159:\"Create beautiful and attracting posts, pages, and landing pages with Gutenberg Blocks and Template Library by Otter. Otter comes with dozens of Gutenb &hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:55:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:3:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=2141548\";s:7:\"caption\";s:13:\"Section Block\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=2141548\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Google Map Block\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-3.gif?rev=2141548\";s:7:\"caption\";s:11:\"Posts Block\";}}s:8:\"versions\";a:21:{s:5:\"1.0.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.0.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.0.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.0\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.0.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.1\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.1.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.2\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.2.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.3\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.3.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.4\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.1.1.4.zip\";s:5:\"1.1.5\";s:61:\"https://downloads.wor