"review-title\">Game changer</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sukafia\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6371eb799baa6d484287c1d38bfc4de?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6371eb799baa6d484287c1d38bfc4de?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sukafia\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Sunday Ukafia <small>(sukafia)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">January 27, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Elementor is a game-changer for website designers. It\'s arguably the best WordPress page builder out there.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:147:\"The most advanced frontend drag &amp; drop page builder. Create high-end, pixel perfect websites at record speeds. Any theme, any page, any design.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:58:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/elementor.2.8.5.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-1.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:119:\"<strong>Drag &amp; Drop.</strong> Our instant drag &amp; drop lets you easily place every element anywhere on the page.\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:62:\"https://ps.w.org/elementor/assets/screenshot-2.gif?rev=1608747\";s:7:\"caption\";s:137:\"<strong>Visual Resize Control.</strong> Customize the